home_whatIsBlalange_text:
The Blålange festival is an annual big party with competitions, talent shows and Celvin.
We work to create an inclusive community that loves party lights. We don't earn anything from the Blålange festival, it's just for fun and the money we get is used for future parties. So join in, you too!
